D%E8%A3%9D%E8%AA%BF%E9%A0%AD%E8%B5%B0-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%B0%B1%E7%AE%97%E5%B7%AE%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%AD%E4%BD%8F%E6%A7%8D%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E7%95%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD%E7%B7%8A%E8%A6%81%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=5232f237\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%BB%8D%E8%A3%9D%E8%AA%BF%E9%A0%AD%E8%B5%B0-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%B0%B1%E7%AE%97%E5%B7%AE%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%AD%E4%BD%8F%E6%A7%8D%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E7%95%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD%E7%B7%8A%E8%A6%81%2F&h=1f109079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/元朗襲擊-回應軍裝調頭走-警方-就算差人孭住槍都會畀人打得好緊要/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩名軍裝警員發現大批人士聚集打鬥，「兩位同事當時係一般巡邏裝備，他們當然有佩槍，（他們）評估過形勢，包括能否進場有效控制在場人士、他們去到後會否令事件更加升溫？會否令其他人士更危險，包括他們自己？所以他們決定要求支援，他們<strong>退守到一個安全位置觀察住</strong>，等候支援部隊。」<br />\n<br />\n縮翻入你老母個閪最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3ef61fd782607753c7af7abc59fea8541b17f6","tid":2118720,"uid":224848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c3404e4cc3c9b79b787a38b2c28a5c3eac64f7","tid":2118720,"uid":123488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"呢個721真係心虛，我指對家"},{"pid":"9d8c80d6d5cdd02e1dc97097c5e9e3584e9e21a4","tid":2118720,"uid":27511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n成班低智狗都可以喺香港政府嘅管治下變成特權階級"},{"pid":"14d3b09fdd28fdf2a064b96cf886cf76159ac3c1","tid":2118720,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ca58f42998c47342d92f824445e47b931d2d964","tid":211872